{"tid":962251,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人覺得洪卓立首《回到最愛的那天》值得更紅？","createTime":"2018-12-30T17:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T17:24:12.000Z","uid":66923,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d99e85275cd3575e2b5bc3f10065692ec78beccb","tid":962251,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"曲唱都幾好 份詞又有意思 個人覺得值得更紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n3lteOg704Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn3lteOg704Q&d=g%2F9XyKfhmpymZxUQnmC8Af7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=fccad831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n3lteOg704Q</a><br />\n作曲：Larry Wong@Public Zoo<br />\n作詞：林若寧<br />\n編曲：Larry Wong@Public Zoo<br />\n監製：舒文@Zoo Music<br />\n<br />\n回到今生最愉快那一秒<br />\n揉合「震撼」「笑容」「眼淚」甜蜜而渺小<br />\n難以捉緊領略箇中美妙<br />\n無論今天敲破你手錶時日要走都抗拒不了<br />\n<br />\n每日同樣過這生活橋<br />\n有多少經典的剎那能做你回味座標<br />\n<br />\n如果可重遇　你最快樂時<br />\n床邊聽父母童話故事<br />\n聯歡會慶祝　壽辰合照時<br />\n頭一次奉獻初吻面帶矜持<br />\n長跑得了獎　決賽勝利時<br />\n還恃時間多幸運未留意<br />\n微細事總有動人事宜<br />\n流逝了之後至不停去追　最浪漫那次<br />\n<br />\n回到當天決定性那一秒<br />\n難道你用鏡頭記住遺憾能變少<br />\n微笑質感裡面有多少奧妙<br />\n無論增加幾百倍變焦無力拍低興奮過心跳<br />\n<br />\n如果可重遇　你最快樂時<br />\n求得她願意同用姓氏<br />\n成婚的那刻　在台上致詞　　<br />\n頭一次望見出世是你嬰兒<br />\n榮登青雲路　你最雀躍時<br />\n還恃時間多幸運未留意<br />\n微細事都有動人事宜<br />\n流逝了之後至不停去追　消失的美意<br />\n<br />\n忙碌的穿梭飛馳　甜美事後至知<br />\n<br />\n重覆的傻事　懺悔那樣遲<br />\n和她不甘認錯離別太易<br />\n陪爸爸喝酒　二人獨處時<br />\n曾想答謝說一句未說經已&hellip;<br />\n回憶的名字　葬禮裡說悼詞<br />\n而過程每天循環而又相似<br />\n快樂只有盡情　及時<br />\n橫豎你生命你都無法知　最後一次"},{"pid":"2e4eeb3e6a7fd0d45e2ce87baef4b3440cd6acf3","tid":962251,"uid":69627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3043d70396baba9f989ac2e5e29d276e6d4073c7","tid":962251,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T17:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf0ce736070a4b8706dbbaa2b31eb72ed43293e","tid":962251,"uid":83397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T19:35:39.000Z","msg":"呢首同少年遊記都比人忽視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d68c37cab349702a3e2a1e050a40faea8bbeb89","tid":962251,"uid":7079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T19:40:31.000Z","msg":"About time?"},{"pid":"e8a9d66bcfae453a7c660cc10b247e8888115a02","tid":962251,"uid":62552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"好鐘意呢首歌"},{"pid":"25bc71d81600a3fb8bc52380572bb1b36d4a3f11","tid":962251,"uid":229094,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"我覺得洪卓立呢個人值得更加紅，唔係淨係指呢一首。<br />\n我個人幾鍾意佢首《彌足珍貴》"},{"pid":"feb52a81f8d290037862dd80804fac2bab5e87b9","tid":962251,"uid":11776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T17:24:12.000Z","msg":"有幾次聽到喊，好有畫面"}]}